        "date": "2025-07-08T00:02:12Z",
        "message": "Release 5.0.0-beta04 (#483)\n\n* Update FDroid deployment script\n\n* Fix deploy script\n\n* Refactor date selector logic\n\n* Update WeekView event style\n\n* Add customizable text style for WeekView events\nFixes #409\n\n* Small refactor\n\n* Add daily messages notification\n\n* Animate selected date scroll\n\n* Fix typos\n\n* Redesign settings categories\n\n* Add Untis API specs and code generators\n\n* Start implementing Untis REST API\n\n* Connect to messages REST API\n\n* Add message display to infocenter\n\n* Parse untis error responses\n\n* Add rudimentary loading placeholder\n\n* WIP Update message item design\n\n* Add click to expand message\n\n* Add event text details\n\n* Add infocenter nav icons\n\n* Add message action button logic\n\n* Fix timetable mapper context type always being STUDENT\n\n* Update custom text color calculation to favor contrast\n\n* Update API spec documentation\n\n* Add error codes\n\n* Add 2FA login support\n\n* Update apiHost handling from login screen input\n\n* Update translations for BetterUntis/String Resources (#476)\n\n* Translate using Weblate (German)\n\nCurrently translated at 100.0% (406 of 406 strings)\n\nTranslation: BetterUntis/String Resources\nTranslate-URL: https://hosted.weblate.org/projects/betteruntis/translations/de/\n\n* Translated using Weblate (German)\n\nCurrently translated at 100.0% (24 of 24 strings)\n\nTranslation: BetterUntis/App Store Metadata\nTranslate-URL: https://hosted.weblate.org/projects/betteruntis/app-store-metadata/de/\n\n* Translate using Weblate (German)\n\nCurrently translated at 100.0% (411 of 411 strings)\n\nTranslation: BetterUntis/String Resources\nTranslate-URL: https://hosted.weblate.org/projects/betteruntis/translations/de/\n\n---------\n\nCo-authored-by: nautilusx <translate@disroot.org>\n\n* Update version to 5.0.0-beta04\n\n---------\n\nCo-authored-by: Weblate (bot) <noreply@weblate.org>\nCo-authored-by: nautilusx <translate@disroot.org>",
